snippet.title: Chef's Tail - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist on Steam:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1498900/Chefs_Tail/


Play as a cat chef in the underworld, give the travelling souls a taste of mortal food. Prepare, gather, fish and learn in this game to get some coins.
